{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013uUSBRszpt4dX2JQumf2TD","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n**Domain** (`internal/domain/workflow.go`): Added `StepTypeWorkflow = \"workflow\"` and `\"workflow_name\"`, `\"prompt_step\"` to `knownStepConfigKeys`.\n\n**Parser** (`internal/dsl/parser.go`): Added type inference for `workflow_name` → `StepTypeWorkflow`, with mutual exclusivity enforcement against `prompt` and `run`.\n\n**HostRunner** (`internal/orchestrator/hostrunner.go`): New file implementing host workflow execution — walks the graph, runs script/agent steps via `exec.Command` with env vars, handles workflow steps by reading previous output, dispatching, and waiting.\n\n**RunWaiter** (`internal/orchestrator/runwaiter.go`): `StoreRunWaiter` polls the run store every 2 seconds until terminal state.\n\n**Orchestrator** (`internal/orchestrator/orchestrator.go`): Added `HostRunner` and `ParseHostWorkflow` fields via functional options. `Run()` checks for `.cloche/host.cloche` — if present, parses and executes via `HostRunner` in a goroutine; otherwise falls back to existing `promptGen → dispatch` path.\n\n**Wiring** (`cmd/cloched/main.go`): Created `StoreRunWaiter` and `HostRunner`, passed to orchestrator via `WithHostRunner`/`WithParseHostWorkflow`.\n\n**Init** (`cmd/cloche/init.go`): Creates `.cloche/host.cloche`, `.cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh` (chmod 0755), `.cloche/scripts/` directory, and `!.cloche/scripts/` gitignore entry.\n\n**Tests**: Parser tests for workflow_name inference and mutual exclusivity; HostRunner tests for script steps, workflow steps, and abort paths; Orchestrator tests verifying host.cloche path vs fallback.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":390,"cache_read_input_tokens":86498,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0